{"tid":682142,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU襯衫搭配吊帶褲超顯高，網友：目測腿長不止2米！","createTime":"2018-05-28T15:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T19:54:32.000Z","uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bea33fbdf49ee0912ac7ca0d288efff646ca63c1","tid":682142,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"一件絲綢襯衫，你會怎麼搭配？可以選擇最簡單的西褲，打造帥氣職場風。亦或者可以選擇一件超短裙，甜美出行。今天的絲綢襯衫IU李知恩出乎意料搭配了一件吊帶褲，網友說，超顯高，目測腿長不止2米！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=794795897,2467911335&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=961&amp;s=3202954D5401835F0A19AAB703008007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D794795897%2C2467911335%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D961%26s%3D3202954D5401835F0A19AAB703008007&h=21fa23ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這件綢緞的襯衫如同IU的肌膚般絲滑，淺V翻領盡顯優雅，高端的藍紫色再配上甜美的荷葉邊袖口，輕熟中又不失少女的甜美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=3635137066,330817477&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=962&amp;s=9CD1A85ADC53C05545823A830300508D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3635137066%2C330817477%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D962%26s%3D9CD1A85ADC53C05545823A830300508D&h=dd78acfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一頂黑色的貝雷帽與吊帶褲顏色保持一致，本身的亮片自帶閃光，混搭風下的IU真的美得好耀眼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=1324467803,2710974652&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=960&amp;s=2B327885C45241D407B4A7830300B087\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1324467803%2C2710974652%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D960%26s%3D2B327885C45241D407B4A7830300B087&h=f59547bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下半身是一件黑色的微喇叭西褲，很好的修飾腿型。類似雪紡的質地，不容易起皺同時又有垂直感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=1013264020,2653536273&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=962&amp;s=0CB2EA170450F26D76AE56870300308D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1013264020%2C2653536273%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D962%26s%3D0CB2EA170450F26D76AE56870300308D&h=eb4765e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來襯衫和西褲就是絕配，可我們IU就是不一樣。在這個基礎上，特地加上兩條吊帶，使得干練中透露出一點小俏皮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=3767133005,1222467046&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=962&amp;s=7AB5E14C86F9B27548EA08900300C08A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3767133005%2C1222467046%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D962%26s%3D7AB5E14C86F9B27548EA08900300C08A&h=bb05ae37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有了小吊帶，再穿上一雙黑色高跟鞋，網友說，超顯高，目測腿長不止2米！估計襯衫要斷貨，大家是時候拿出壓箱底的背帶褲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=3384741993,1684471874&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=962&amp;s=E6A095438E1210D649818C9F03001004\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3384741993%2C1684471874%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D962%26s%3DE6A095438E1210D649818C9F03001004&h=992dd0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全身上下的服裝搭配只有藍紫色和黑色兩種顏色，簡約卻不簡單！你喜歡混搭風下的IU李知恩嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=853952709,1536372910&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=962&amp;s=78229C55CC5274D6430DC28A0300A017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D853952709%2C1536372910%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D962%26s%3D78229C55CC5274D6430DC28A0300A017&h=d041410b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"794fece3941bdfc67ef3632c85602ff09506d769","tid":682142,"uid":158977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"釘呢"},{"pid":"cc55913f587a3e473519aa4a305373396792733e","tid":682142,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"你估佢自己襯嘅咩"},{"pid":"6d8d681acef224d606d2eb6ffa01de1f782